Class SwitchPage

java.lang.Object
com.example.mycasinofx.controllers.switchPage.SwitchPage
All Implemented Interfaces:
PageSwitchInterface
public class SwitchPage extends Object implements PageSwitchInterface
The SwitchPage class implements the PageSwitchInterface to provide methods for switching between pages in the application.
